   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-2-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-2-c" mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>明白是什么意思吗?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$古代文字的内容$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>勇敢的后裔，从卑鄙的红色团伙和黑色翅膀帮里拯救先知吧。</FONT><BR><FONT color=#a82424></FONT><BR>- <FONT color=#7e12d2>比萨斯 阿罗诺比乌斯</FONT> -</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-2-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-2-d" mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>另外的预言?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$纹章学者贝利$<BR>比萨斯在古代语是指<FONT color=#a82424>贤者</FONT>，阿罗诺比乌斯是指<FONT color=#a94407>贤者阿罗诺</FONT>的名字。<BR>真让人惊讶…。<BR>这是贤者留下的另外一个<FONT color=#a82424>预言</FONT>呢</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-2-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-2-e" mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>（继续）</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$纹章学者贝利$<BR>是的。这里的<FONT color=#a82424>命运之轮发挥光芒</FONT>的语句是指先知与遗迹产生反应时的时期。而<BR><FONT color=#a82424>继承者</FONT>是指继承贤者法杖的弟子们。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-2-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-2-f" mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>是不是指劫持先知的黑骑士啊?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$纹章学者贝利$<BR>不过，不知<FONT color=#a82424>黑色翅膀</FONT>是指什么。卑鄙的红色团伙应该是指红色鹰身人和魔物们吧，但是黑色翅膀的话…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-2-f" image="QN_Npc_Velskud1.dds" itemindex="">
